{"word":"G4823 - συμβουλεύω - symbouleúō - soom-bool-yoo'-o - Consult","slug":"G4823","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμβουλεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>symbouleúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soom-bool-yoo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Consult"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03B2;&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - sumbouleuo&#x0304;</b> - <i>soom-bool-yoo'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G1011\">G1011</a>; to <i>give</i> (or <i>take</i>) <i>advice jointly</i>, that is, <i>recommend</i>, <i>deliberate</i> or <i>determine:</i> - consult, (give, take) counsel (together)."}]}